metadata.name: #1 // R. LOCKJAW
metadata.description:
"I’ve been living in the cage all my life. Quiet life, maybe. But when a bag or rice is only enough so much for seven of your families, you need to find the gold somewhere. Thankfully my fist talks better even when I’m hungry. The Highrisers have ‘tis boxing stuff on the dark alley, every primetime till midnight weekend…I believe you know the rest."

(Rina then show me the belt from the infamous 'Class of 2020 Boxing Championship')

-----

2480x3508. PNG. Digital on Procreate and Photoshop. 2021-2022.
